"That login name didn’t work.\n"
"Please try again."
msgstr ""
"See kasutajanimi ei toimi sisselogimisel.\n"
"Palun proovi uuesti."

#: panels/user-accounts/cc-add-user-dialog.c:1173
msgid ""
"That login password didn’t work.\n"
"Please try again."
msgstr ""
"See salasõna ei toimi sisselogimisel.\n"
"Palun proovi uuesti."

